Global Helicopter Skid Landing Gear Market Insights
Helicopter Skid Landing Gear Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Helicopter Skid Landing Gear Market Overview
The helicopter skid landing gear market is anticipated to reach a value of USD 1.3 billion by 2030, growing at a significant CAGR over the forecast period. This market growth is driven by increasing demand for helicopters in various sectors such as military, search and rescue, and commercial aviation. The versatility, cost-efficiency, and ability to operate in rugged environments are key factors enhancing the popularity of skid landing gear in helicopter designs. Additionally, innovations in materials and manufacturing techniques are expected to boost product performance and reduce operational costs, driving market growth.

